---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "AboutPage",
  "name": "About The Candle Sleeves",
  "description": "Learn about The Candle Sleeves — a US-based premium custom candle packaging company serving candle brands nationwide.",
  "url": "https://thecandlesleeves.com/about"
};
---

<Layout
  title="About The Candle Sleeves | Premium Custom Candle Packaging USA"
  description="Learn about The Candle Sleeves — America's trusted source for premium custom candle sleeve packaging. Discover our story, values, and commitment to quality."
  canonical="https://thecandlesleeves.com/about"
  schema={schema}
>
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
      <h1>Crafting Packaging That Tells Your Brand Story</h1>
      <p>We are a passionate team of packaging specialists dedicated to helping candle brands across the USA stand out on every shelf and in every unboxing moment.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="gap:4rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
          <h2>Born from a Passion for Beautiful Packaging</h2>
          <p>The Candle Sleeves was founded with a single conviction: great candles deserve packaging that matches their quality. Too many exceptional candle brands were losing sales not because of their product, but because their packaging failed to communicate the premium experience inside.</p>
          <p>We set out to change that. Starting with a focused specialization in candle sleeve packaging, we built a company from the ground up around one niche — and we mastered it. Today, we serve hundreds of candle brands across the United States, from independent artisan makers to established retail lines, all with the same commitment to craft and quality.</p>
          <p>Our headquarters in Bloomington, Illinois gives us a central location to serve candle businesses from coast to coast with reliable, fast shipping and personalized account support. We are not a generic packaging factory — we are specialists, and that focus shows in every sleeve we produce.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/products/candle-gift-sleeves.jpg" alt="Premium candle gift sleeves by The Candle Sleeves" style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);width:100%;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <span class="section-label">Mission & Values</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">What Drives Everything We Do</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Our values are not words on a wall. They are the principles that guide every decision we make, every design we approve, and every order we ship.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#127775;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Quality Without Compromise</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">We use only premium materials — from FSC-certified cardboard to rigid chipboard — and our printing meets the highest industry standards. Every order is quality-inspected before it leaves our facility.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#129309;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Partnership, Not Transactions</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">We take time to understand each brand we work with. Our packaging specialists become genuine partners in your business — offering guidance on materials, finishes, and design to achieve the best possible result.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#127807;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Sustainability Matters</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">We believe in responsible packaging. Our <a href="/eco-friendly-candle-sleeves" class="internal-link">eco-friendly candle sleeves</a> use recycled and FSC-certified materials, and we continuously work to reduce waste across our production process.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#9889;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Speed & Reliability</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">We know that packaging delays can stall product launches and cost sales. Our streamlined production process means quotes within 24 hours, fast production runs, and on-time delivery you can count on.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#127919;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Precision in Every Detail</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">From the exact dieline cut to your candle jar, to the color accuracy of your brand palette — we are obsessive about the details that make packaging truly exceptional and shelf-worthy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-box" style="flex-direction:column;background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
          <div class="icon-box__icon" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">&#128140;</div>
          <div>
            <div class="icon-box__title" style="font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Transparent Communication</div>
            <div class="icon-box__text">No hidden fees, no surprise timelines. We communicate clearly at every stage of your order — from initial quote through design approval, production, and delivery.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="section--sm section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box__num">500+</div>
          <div class="stat-box__label">Brands Served</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box__num">14+</div>
          <div class="stat-box__label">Sleeve Types</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box__num">50</div>
          <div class="stat-box__label">States Delivered</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-box__num">100%</div>
          <div class="stat-box__label">Satisfaction Goal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Materials Commitment -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="gap:4rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <img src="/images/products/cardboard-candle-sleeves.jpg" alt="Premium cardboard candle sleeves materials" style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);width:100%;" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Our Materials</span>
          <h2 style="color:var(--gold-light);">A Commitment to Premium Substrates</h2>
          <p style="color:rgba(250,246,239,0.85);">The foundation of great packaging is the material it is made from. We have carefully sourced our supply chain to offer a range of premium substrates for every brand need and budget.</p>
          <ul style="color:rgba(250,246,239,0.8);list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);">&#10003;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color:var(--gold-light);">FSC-Certified Cardboard</strong> — Responsibly sourced, excellent printability</li>
            <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);">&#10003;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color:var(--gold-light);">Natural Kraft Paper</strong> — Recyclable, earthy aesthetic for artisan brands</li>
            <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);">&#10003;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color:var(--gold-light);">Corrugated Board</strong> — Superior protection for shipping applications</li>
            <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);">&#10003;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color:var(--gold-light);">Rigid Chipboard</strong> — 2mm+ thickness for premium retail presentation</li>
            <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);">&#10003;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color:var(--gold-light);">Recycled Content Board</strong> — Post-consumer recycled fiber for eco-conscious brands</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <span class="section-label">How We Work</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Simple 4-Step Process</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">We have refined our workflow to make custom candle packaging as simple and stress-free as possible for every brand we serve.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2" style="gap:3rem;">
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Request a Free Quote</h3>
              <p>Share your project details through our <a href="/quote" class="internal-link">quote form</a> or by calling us directly. We respond within 24 hours with a detailed, competitive pricing breakdown.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Design Consultation & Artwork</h3>
              <p>Our packaging specialists review your requirements and create a custom dieline and digital proof. You have unlimited revisions until the design is exactly right.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Production & Quality Control</h3>
              <p>Once you approve the proof, we move into production. Every batch goes through a rigorous quality inspection — checking print accuracy, structural integrity, and finish quality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-num">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Delivery Nationwide</h3>
              <p>Your finished candle sleeves are carefully packed and shipped to your door anywhere in the USA. You receive tracking information so you always know where your order is.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Philosophy -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <span class="section-label">Our Philosophy</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">We Believe Packaging Is Your Brand's First Voice</h2>
      <p style="font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Before a customer lights your candle, before they smell its fragrance, before they experience everything your brand offers — they see the sleeve. That moment of visual contact is your first opportunity to communicate quality, craft, and character.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray);">We take that responsibility seriously. Whether you are ordering <a href="/luxury-candle-sleeves" class="internal-link">luxury candle sleeves</a> for a high-end boutique collection or <a href="/kraft-candle-sleeves" class="internal-link">kraft candle sleeves</a> for a farmers market brand, every order receives the same level of attention, expertise, and care.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Get in Touch with Our Team &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Elevate Your Candle Brand?</h2>
      <p>Join hundreds of candle businesses across the USA that trust The Candle Sleeves for their packaging needs.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/quote" class="btn btn--dark" style="background:white;color:var(--gold-dark);">Request a Free Quote &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn--outline">Browse All Products</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
